sney company he served as the president of espn domestic focus new york since november   he served as the president of espn all domestic  intl operations since march   he joined espn in  january  and served as its executive vice president of sales  marketing since september  he oversaw the launch of  new networks he began his espn career in the administration department and served several executive positions in espns affiliate sales and marketing area since january   he was responsible for affiliate sales advertising sales marketing and research for all of espns domestic networks in  he joined the affiliate marketing staff as marketing representative for espns south central region and served as its marketing representative central region since may  mr bodenheimer served as national accounts manager of the rocky mountain region at espn since july  and director of affiliate sales eastern division since february  at espn he served as vice president of affiliate sales for eastern division since july  and vice president of national affiliate sales since june  he served as vice president of affiliate sales and marketing since november  and senior vice president of affiliate sales and marketing of espn since october  he served as senior vice president of sales and marketing of espn since may  he served as cochairman of disney media networks unit of walt disney co from april   to december   he served as an executive chairman of espn inc at disney interactive studios inc since january   he served as cochairman of disneys media networks from april  to december   he has been independent director of under armour inc since august  mr bodenheimer has been a director at sirius xm holdings inc since september  and sirius xm radio inc since september   he serves as a director at the advertising council inc he serves on the boards of ncta the national cable telecommunications association cable in the classroom the v foundation for cancer research he served as a director of disneys media networks until december   he served as a director of disneys media networks unit until december   he was named the  sports industrialist of the year the highest honor given by the sports business daily the sporting news selected him as s most powerful person in sports the list ranks those who wield the most influence in the world of sports also in  the greater new york march of dimes recognized him with its corporate leadership award he is a member of the cable programming committee of the museum of television and radio mr bodenheimer graduated from denison university in  with a bachelor of arts degree in economicsread full background corporate headquarters  hull streetbaltimore maryland united statesphone fax  board members memberships chairmanespn incdirectorthe advertising council incpresentdirectorsirius xm holdings incpresentmember of the board of directorssirius xm radio incpresentindependent directorunder armour inc education ba denison university other affiliations espn incsirius xm holdings incthe walt disney companydenison universitythe advertising council incdisney interactive studios incsirius xm radio inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepositioncompanycompensationlaura j alber ceo president  directorwilliamssonoma incmrobert greenberg cofounder chairman of the board and chief executive officerskechers usa incmsimon a wolfson chief executive officer and executive directornext plckrobert v vitale chief